IPTables-Rule version 0.03
==========================

IPTables::Rule is for holding netfilter rule criteria in objects.
	=> Supports IPv4 and IPv6
	=> Convert object into CLI command
	=> Basic validation of input performed
	=> Modules automatically enabled when required

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  None

